data.description: A beautiful home maintained by the original owners since purchasing brand new in 1986, in the heart of Archdale landing. Open family living and dining, as well as formal dining and living areas on the first floor. Beautiful counter tops throughout. Large fenced in backyard with a screened in back porch. New HVAC installed in 2016, new roof installed in 2015. Don't miss this amazing opportunity to call Archdale Landing Home!A $1100 Lender Credit is available and will be applied towards the buyer's closing costs and pre-paids if the buyer chooses to use the seller's preferred lender. This credit is in addition to any negotiated seller concessions.*If square footage matters please measure - measurements taken from tax records - if school matters - please confirm with the school directly*
